    "data": [
        {
            "title": "安世中國指責荷蘭部分管理層惡意阻撓 內部交鋒依然激烈",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 安世的中國子公司表示，荷蘭母公司斷供晶圓，干擾安世中國生產經營，這顯示，儘管旨在恢復重要汽車零組件供應的政治努力仍在繼續，但公司內部交鋒依然激烈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">安世中國致信員工稱，荷蘭部分管理層採取斷供晶圓等方式惡意阻撓、干擾安世中國生產經營，不按約定向安世中國撥付資金和提供必要的支持。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「公司絕無任何‘惡意意圖’，」安世總部發言人周五在電子郵件聲明中表示，「公司將繼續秉持透明原則，保障業務連續性和客戶的利益。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-78513194-9010-34b0-adbe-580e1150dd72-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷蘭方面此前曾表示，付款糾紛導致晶圓斷供。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家總部位於荷蘭的晶片製造商為中國公司聞泰科技旗下企業，供應寶馬、福斯汽車等車企使用的功率控制晶片。這類零組件短缺已擾亂歐洲及其他地區的生產。安世內部關係吃緊可能會讓恢復從中國出口零組件的政治努力變得更加複雜。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Nexperia Accused of Meddling by Chinese Unit as Spat Drags On</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Sarah Jacob.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AE%89%E4%B8%96%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%8C%87%E8%B2%AC%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E9%98%BB%E6%92%93-%E5%85%A7%E9%83%A8%E4%BA%A4%E9%8B%92%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E6%BF%80%E7%83%88-170741841.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-15 01:45:57",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
